{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853629234,"sessionID":"ses_286e04ae0ffeYViPRjofjXV87z","part":{"id":"prt_d791feabe001MGMMUucVx6hTnW","messageID":"msg_d791fe056001uFPD9ezSKbo8AB","sessionID":"ses_286e04ae0ffeYViPRjofjXV87z","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1d07f969e52a491d93a0d960","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-021 — CLI build 命令\n2: \n3: **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: **Language:** Python\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `build` 子命令，从已 pack 的工作空间构建容器镜像。`build` 命令读取 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中的构建配置，验证前置条件（Docker 可用性、Dockerfile 存在），执行本地 Docker 构建或触发云端构建，自动管理镜像版本标签，并将构建结果持久化回元数据文件。\n10: \n11: 当前 Python CLI 已定义 `build` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `BuildRuntime` 类结构，但需要完整实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为，包括版本自增、前置校验、本地/云端构建分发和元数据更新。\n12: \n13: ## 范围\n14: \n15: ### 包含\n16: \n17: 1. **`build` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n18:    - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `proxy` (`-p`), `cloud_provider` (`--cloud-provider`), `output` (`--output`), `verbose` (`--verbose`)\n19:    - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示镜像名称、标签、构建时间\n20:    - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1\n21:    - Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n22: \n23: 2. **`BuildRuntime` 类完整实现** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\n24:    - `build(workspace_path, **options)` — 主入口，编排完整构建流程\n25:    - `_increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)` — 自增版本号（patch bump `X.Y.Z` → `X.Y.(Z+1)`，无版本用 `0.0.1`，非标准格式追加 `.1` 或 `{version}-1`），构建失败时回滚\n26:    - `_validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path)` — 验证 `agent_metadata.yaml` 存在、`Dockerfile` 已生成、local 模式下 Docker 可用\n27:    - `_build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 使用 `DockerService.build_image()` 执行本地 Docker 构建，proxy 通过 `build_args` 传递\n28:    - `_build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 根据 `cloud_provider` 调用云厂商构建 API\n29:    - `_update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, build_result, tag)` — 更新 `metadata.image` 字段并持久化\n30: \n31: 3. **`DockerService` 构建相关方法** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n32:    - `check_docker_available()` — 检查 Docker 守护进程是否运行\n33:    - `build_image(dockerfile_path, context_path, image_name, tag, build_args)` — 构建镜像并返回 `{\"image_name\", \"image_id\", \"image_size\", \"build_time\"}`\n34:    - `_format_size(size_bytes)` — 格式化镜像大小显示\n35: \n36: ### 不包含\n37: \n38: - `pack` 命令的实现（由 AR-020 覆盖）\n39: - `publish` 命令的实现 — 依赖 build 输出的镜像，由其他 AR 覆盖\n40: - `DockerService.push_image()` 和 `remove_image()` 的完整实现 — build 阶段仅构建，推送由 publish 处理\n41: - `KubernetesProvider` / `AgentCubeProvider` 实现\n42: - 云端构建的具体云厂商适配器实现（仅定义接口/占位）\n43: - CI/CD pipeline 变更\n44: \n45: ## 架构概要\n46: \n47: ### 组件关系\n48: \n49: ```\n50: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n51: │                    CLI Layer (Typer)                     │\n52: │  agentcube/cli/main.py: build() command                  │\n53: │  - 解析选项 → 调用 BuildRuntime.build()                  │\n54: │  - Rich 输出 / _handle_error()                           │\n55: └──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘\n56:                        │\n57: ┌──────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────┐\n58: │                   Runtime Layer                          │\n59: │  agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py: BuildRuntime        │\n60: │  - 版本自增 → 前置校验 → 构建 → 元数据更新               │\n61: │  - 依赖 DockerService 执行本地构建                       │\n62: │  - 依赖 MetadataService 加载/保存元数据                  │\n63: └───────┬──────────────────────────────────┬──────────────┘\n64:         │                                  │\n65: ┌───────▼──────────┐          ┌────────────▼──────────────┐\n66: │  Service Layer   │          │  Metadata Layer           │\n67: │  DockerService   │          │  MetadataService          │\n68: │  - Docker SDK    │          │  - YAML I/O               │\n69: │  - build_image   │          │  - 版本回滚支持            │\n70: └──────────────────┘          └───────────────────────────┘\n71: ```\n72: \n73: ### 构建流程\n74: \n75: ```\n76: build() CLI\n77:   │\n78:   ├── BuildRuntime.build()\n79:   │     │\n80:   │     ├── 1. 加载 agent_metadata.yaml\n81:   │     │\n82:   │     ├── 2. _increment_version() — 自增版本号\n83:   │     │\n84:   │     ├── 3. _validate_build_prerequisites()\n85:   │     │     ├── metadata 存在?\n86:   │     │     ├── Dockerfile 存在?\n87:   │     │     └── Docker 可用? (local 模式)\n88:   │     │\n89:   │     ├── 4. 根据 build_mode 分发\n90:   │     │     ├── \"local\"  → _build_local()\n91:   │     │     │     └── DockerService.build_image()\n92:   │     │     └── \"cloud\" → _build_cloud()\n93:   │     │           └── 云厂商 API 调用\n94:   │     │\n95:   │     ├── 5. 成功 → _update_build_metadata()\n96:   │     │     └── 保存 metadata.image = {name, id, tag}\n97:   │     │\n98:   │     └── 失败 → 回滚版本号 → 抛出异常\n99:   │\n100:   └── CLI 输出: 镜像名称、标签、构建时间\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ### 目录结构（新增/修改的文件）\n104: \n105: ```\n106: cmd/cli/\n107: ├── agentcube/\n108: │   ├── cli/\n109: │   │   └── main.py                # 修改: 实现 build() 命令体\n110: │   ├── runtime/\n111: │   │   └── build_runtime.py       # 实现: BuildRuntime 类\n112: │   └── services/\n113: │       └── docker_service.py      # 实现: check_docker_available, build_image\n114: ```\n115: \n116: ## 影响分析\n117: \n118: ### 直接影响\n119: \n120: | 文件 | 变更类型 | 说明 |\n121: |------|----------|------|\n122: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | 修改 | 实现 `build()` 命令体，调用 `BuildRuntime` |\n123: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | 实现 | 完整实现所有方法 |\n124: | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | 实现 | Docker 检查、构建、大小格式化 |\n125: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 确认 | 确保 load/save 支持版本回滚场景 |\n126: \n127: ### 上游依赖（本变更依赖的已完成组件）\n128: \n129: - **AR-020 (`pack` 命令)** — 依赖 pack 生成的 `Dockerfile` 和 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n130: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0` — CLI 框架（已有依赖）\n131: - `pydantic>=2.0.0` — 元数据验证（已有依赖）\n132: - `pyyaml>=6.0` — YAML 序列化（已有依赖）\n133: - `docker>=6.0.0` — Docker SDK for Python（已有依赖）\n134: - `rich>=13.0.0` — Progress spinner、格式化输出（已有依赖）\n135: - `semver>=3.0.0` — 语义化版本解析和自增（已有依赖）\n136: \n137: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n138: \n139: - **AR: `publish` 命令** — 依赖 build 产出的容器镜像进行发布/部署\n140: - **AR: `invoke` 命令** — 间接依赖 build（通过 publish 部署后的 endpoint）\n141: \n142: ### 无影响的组件\n143: \n144: - `PackRuntime` — 本 AR 不修改 pack 逻辑\n145: - `PublishRuntime`、`InvokeRuntime`、`StatusRuntime` — 本 AR 不修改\n146: - `KubernetesProvider` / `AgentCubeProvider` — 不涉及\n147: - Go 二进制入口 (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) — 独立实现\n148: \n149: ### 风险评估\n150: \n151: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n152: |------|------|----------|\n153: | Docker 守护进程未运行导致构建失败 | 高 | 前置校验 `_validate_build_prerequisites` 提前检查，给出清晰错误提示 |\n154: | 版本回滚失败导致 metadata 不一致 | 中 | 使用临时变量保存原始版本号，确保异常路径也执行回滚 |\n155: | 大镜像构建超时或占用过多磁盘 | 中 | Docker SDK stream 日志显示进度；后续可添加磁盘空间检查 |\n156: | 云端构建异步完成，状态不确定 | 中 | 云端构建返回 job_id，用户通过 `status` 命令查询构建状态 |\n157: | proxy URL 格式无效导致依赖下载失败 | 低 | Docker build_args 传递，Docker 自身会报错；可在 CLI 层增加 URL 格式校验 |\n158: \n159: ## 备选方案\n160: \n161: ### 1. BuildRuntime 类编排所有构建步骤（✅ 选定方案）\n162: \n163: **做法**：`BuildRuntime` 类包含所有私有方法，在 `build()` 中顺序调用，与 `PackRuntime` 模式一致。\n164: \n165: **优点**：\n166: - 与 AR-020 的 `PackRuntime` 架构一致，降低认知负担\n167: - 逻辑集中，易于调试和测试\n168: - 与 spec 中定义的类结构完全匹配\n169: \n170: **缺点**：\n171: - 类包含多种职责（版本管理、校验、构建、元数据更新）\n172: - 云端构建逻辑可能与本地构建差异较大\n173: \n174: **决策**：采用。与现有 spec 和 pack 命令架构一致，Size M 范围内可控。\n175: \n176: ### 2. 构建策略模式分离本地/云端\n177: \n178: **做法**：定义 `BuildStrategy` 接口，`LocalBuildStrategy` 和 `CloudBuildStrategy` 实现，`BuildRuntime` 委托给策略。\n179: \n180: **优点**：\n181: - 本地和云端构建逻辑完全隔离\n182: - 添加新构建方式（如 remote Docker daemon）只需新策略\n183: \n184: **缺点**：\n185: - 增加抽象层，对当前仅 2 种构建模式来说过度设计\n186: - 与 spec 中定义的 `_build_local` / `_build_cloud` 私有方法结构不一致\n187: \n188: **决策**：不采用。当前仅支持 local/cloud，策略模式增加复杂度。可在未来添加第 3 种构建方式时重构。\n189: \n190: ### 3. 版本自增放在 pack 阶段\n191: \n192: **做法**：pack 时就确定版本号，build 使用固定版本。\n193: \n194: **优点**：\n195: - 版本号在 pack 时确定，build 更简单\n196: - 用户可以在 pack 后预览版本号\n197: \n198: **缺点**：\n199: - 多次 build 会产生相同版本号的镜像，无法区分\n200: - 违反\"每次构建产生唯一产物\"的原则\n201: - 与 spec 中\"build 时自增版本\"的要求不符\n202: \n203: **决策**：不采用。build 阶段每次执行都生成新镜像，版本号应在 build 时自增。\n204: \n205: ## 实现要点\n206: \n207: ### `build` 命令流程\n208: \n209: ```python\n210: @app.command()\n211: def build(\n212:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...),\n213:     proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\", ...),\n214:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", ...),\n215:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", ...),\n216:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...),\n217: ) -> None:\n218:     workspace_path = Path(workspace).resolve()\n219:     try:\n220:         with Progress() as progress:\n221:             task = progress.add_task(\"Building...\", total=None)\n222:             runtime = BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n223:             result = runtime.build(workspace_path,\n224:                 proxy=proxy,\n225:                 cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n226:                 output=output,\n227:             )\n228:         # Rich 输出: image_name, tag, build_time\n229:     except Exception as e:\n230:         _handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)\n231: ```\n232: \n233: ### `BuildRuntime.build()` 内部流程\n234: \n235: ```python\n236: def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n237:     # 1. 加载元数据\n238:     metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n239: \n240:     # 2. 自增版本号\n241:     original_version = metadata.version\n242:     self._increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)\n243: \n244:     try:\n245:         # 3. 前置校验\n246:         self._validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path)\n247: \n248:         # 4. 根据 build_mode 分发\n249:         if metadata.build_mode == \"local\":\n250:             build_result = self._build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n251:         else:\n252:             build_result = self._build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n253: \n254:         # 5. 更新元数据\n255:         tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n256:         self._update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, build_result, tag)\n257: \n258:         return build_result\n259: \n260:     except Exception:\n261:         # 回滚版本号\n262:         metadata.version = original_version\n263:         self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n264:         raise\n265: ```\n266: \n267: ### 版本自增逻辑\n268: \n269: ```python\n270: def _increment_version(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata) -> Any:\n271:     current = metadata.version\n272:     if not current:\n273:         metadata.version = \"0.0.1\"\n274:     elif re.match(r\"^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$\", current):\n275:         # X.Y.Z → X.Y.(Z+1)\n276:         parts = current.split(\".\")\n277:         parts[2] = str(int(parts[2]) + 1)\n278:         metadata.version = \".\".join(parts)\n279:     else:\n280:         # 非标准格式: 追加 .1 或 {version}-1\n281:         try:\n282:             v = semver.Version.parse(current)\n283:             metadata.version = str(v.bump_patch())\n284:         except ValueError:\n285:             metadata.version = f\"{current}-1\"\n286: ```\n287: \n288: ### Docker 前置校验\n289: \n290: ```python\n291: def _validate_build_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None:\n292:     metadata_path = workspace_path / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\n293:     if not metadata_path.exists():\n294:         raise ValueError(f\"Metadata file not found: {metadata_path}\")\n295: \n296:     dockerfile_path = workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"\n297:     if not dockerfile_path.exists():\n298:         raise ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found. Run 'pack' first.\")\n299: \n300:     docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n301:     if not docker_service.check_docker_available():\n302:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n303: ```\n304: \n305: ### 本地构建实现\n306: \n307: ```python\n308: def _build_local(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n309:     docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n310:     image_name = metadata.image.get(\"name\", metadata.agent_name) if metadata.image else metadata.agent_name\n311:     tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n312: \n313:     build_args = None\n314:     if options.get(\"proxy\"):\n315:         build_args = {\"HTTP_PROXY\": options[\"proxy\"], \"HTTPS_PROXY\": options[\"proxy\"]}\n316: \n317:     dockerfile_path = workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"\n318:     result = docker_service.build_image(\n319:         dockerfile_path=dockerfile_path,\n320:         context_path=workspace_path,\n321:         image_name=image_name,\n322:         tag=tag,\n323:         build_args=build_args,\n324:     )\n325:     return result\n326: ```\n327: \n328: ### `DockerService.check_docker_available()`\n329: \n330: ```python\n331: def check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n332:     try:\n333:         client = docker.from_env()\n334:         client.ping()\n335:         return True\n336:     except Exception:\n337:         return False\n338: ```\n339: \n340: ### `DockerService.build_image()`\n341: \n342: ```python\n343: def build_image(self, dockerfile_path: Path, context_path: Path,\n344:                 image_name: str, tag: str = \"latest\",\n345:                 build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Dict[str, str]:\n346:     client = docker.from_env()\n347:     start_time = time.time()\n348: \n349:     image, logs = client.images.build(\n350:         path=str(context_path),\n351:         dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path),\n352:         tag=f\"{image_name}:{tag}\",\n353:         buildargs=build_args,\n354:     )\n355: \n356:     build_time = time.time() - start_time\n357:     image_info = client.images.get(image.id)\n358: \n359:     return {\n360:         \"image_name\": image_name,\n361:         \"image_id\": image.short_id,\n362:         \"image_size\": self._format_size(image_info.attrs.get(\"Size\", 0)),\n363:         \"build_time\": f\"{build_time:.2f}s\",\n364:     }\n365: ```\n366: \n367: ## 验收标准\n368: \n369: - [ ] `build` 命令接受所有指定选项，使用正确默认值\n370: - [ ] `workspace` 默认 `.`，可通过 `-f` / `--workspace` 覆盖\n371: - [ ] `proxy` 可通过 `-p` / `--proxy` 指定，作为 Docker build args 传递\n372: - [ ] `build_mode` 为 `local` 时，Docker 不可用抛出 `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n373: - [ ] `build_mode` 为 `local` 时，Dockerfile 不存在抛出明确错误提示\n374: - [ ] 版本号自增：`X.Y.Z` → `X.Y.(Z+1)`；无版本 → `0.0.1`；非标准格式 fallback\n375: - [ ] 构建失败时版本号回滚到原始值\n376: - [ ] 构建成功后更新 `metadata.image` 字段（image_name, image_id, tag）\n377: - [ ] 成功消息显示镜像名称、标签、构建时间（Rich 格式）\n378: - [ ] 错误处理打印红色消息 + traceback（verbose），退出码 1\n379: - [ ] Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n380: - [ ] `--verbose` 启用详细日志输出\n381: - [ ] `cloud_provider` 选项在 cloud 模式下生效（可传参给云端构建）\n382: - [ ] `--output` 选项支持指定构建产物输出路径\n383: \n384: ## 状态\n385: \n386: - [ ] 提案审查\n387: - [ ] 实现\n388: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 388 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-021 — CLI build 命令\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli\n**Language:** Python\n**Size:** M\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `build` 子命令，从已 pack 的工作空间构建容器镜像。`build` 命令读取 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中的构建配置，验证前置条件（Docker 可用性、Dockerfile 存在），执行本地 Docker 构建或触发云端构建，自动管理镜像版本标签，并将构建结果持久化回元数据文件。\n\n当前 Python CLI 已定义 `build` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `BuildRuntime` 类结构，但需要完整实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为，包括版本自增、前置校验、本地/云端构建分发和元数据更新。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. **`build` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n   - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `proxy` (`-p`), `cloud_provider` (`--cloud-provider`), `output` (`--output`), `verbose` (`--verbose`)\n   - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示镜像名称、标签、构建时间\n   - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775853629202,"end":1775853629231}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853630472,"sessionID":"ses_286e04ae0ffeYViPRjofjXV87z","part":{"id":"prt_d791fefb7001fRyUyZhUm4WQsb","messageID":"msg_d791fe056001uFPD9ezSKbo8AB","sessionID":"ses_286e04ae0ffeYViPRjofjXV87z","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ff7e31adfa5d477ea16bcf8d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-021: CLI build 命令 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n6: - **Language:** Python\n7: - **Size:** M\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: `build` command entry point\n13: \n14: The system SHALL provide a `build` subcommand on the Typer application that orchestrates container image creation from a previously packaged workspace.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Command signature and options\n17: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and the user runs `agentcube build --help`\n18: - **WHEN** the help text is displayed\n19: - **THEN** it SHALL show the following options:\n20:   - `-f, --workspace TEXT` — Path to the agent workspace directory (default: `.`)\n21:   - `-p, --proxy TEXT` — Custom proxy URL for dependency resolution\n22:   - `--cloud-provider TEXT` — Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\n23:   - `--output TEXT` — Output path for build artifacts\n24:   - `--verbose` — Enable detailed logging\n25: \n26: #### Scenario: Default option values\n27: - **GIVEN** the user runs `agentcube build` with no options\n28: - **WHEN** the command resolves its arguments\n29: - **THEN** the values SHALL be:\n30:   - `workspace` = `\".\"`\n31:   - `proxy` = `None`\n32:   - `cloud_provider` = `None`\n33:   - `output` = `None`\n34:   - `verbose` = `False`\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: Workspace path resolution\n37: - **GIVEN** the user provides a workspace path via `-f` or `--workspace`\n38: - **WHEN** the command starts execution\n39: - **THEN** the path SHALL be resolved to an absolute `Path` object before being passed to `BuildRuntime`\n40: \n41: ### Requirement: Build mode resolution\n42: \n43: The system SHALL determine the build strategy (local vs cloud) from workspace metadata, with CLI overrides taking precedence.\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: Default to local build mode\n46: - **GIVEN** a workspace with `agent_metadata.yaml` containing `build_mode: local` (or no `build_mode` field)\n47: - **WHEN** the `build` command runs without `--cloud-provider`\n48: - **THEN** the system SHALL execute a local Docker build via `BuildRuntime._build_local`\n49: \n50: #### Scenario: Cloud build mode via cloud provider flag\n51: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--cloud-provider huawei`\n52: - **WHEN** the command resolves the build mode\n53: - **THEN** the system SHALL execute a cloud build via `BuildRuntime._build_cloud` regardless of metadata `build_mode`\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: Cloud build mode from metadata\n56: - **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` contains `build_mode: cloud`\n57: - **WHEN** the `build` command runs without `--cloud-provider`\n58: - **THEN** the system SHALL execute a cloud build via `BuildRuntime._build_cloud`\n59: \n60: ### Requirement: Build prerequisites validation\n61: \n62: The system SHALL validate all prerequisites before attempting a build.\n63: \n64: #### Scenario: Docker availability check for local builds\n65: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local`\n66: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._validate_build_prerequisites` runs\n67: - **THEN** it SHALL call `DockerService.check_docker_available()` and raise `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")` if Docker is unavailable\n68: \n69: #### Scenario: Workspace packaging validation\n70: - **GIVEN** the workspace has not been packaged (no `agent_metadata.yaml` exists)\n71: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime.build` is called\n72: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the workspace must be packaged first\n73: \n74: #### Scenario: Metadata load success\n75: - **GIVEN** a valid `agent_metadata.yaml` exists in the workspace\n76: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime.build` loads metadata\n77: - **THEN** it SHALL use `MetadataService.load_metadata` to parse the file into an `AgentMetadata` object\n78: \n79: ### Requirement: Version increment on build\n80: \n81: The system SHALL automatically increment the semantic version in metadata before building and handle rollback on failure.\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Patch version increment\n84: - **GIVEN** `metadata.version` is `\"1.2.3\"` (valid semver `X.Y.Z`)\n85: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._increment_version` runs\n86: - **THEN** the version SHALL become `\"1.2.4\"` (patch bumped)\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: Append `.1` for non-semver versions\n89: - **GIVEN** `metadata.version` is `\"1.0-beta\"` (not valid semver)\n90: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._increment_version` runs\n91: - **THEN** the version SHALL become `\"1.0-beta.1\"`\n92: \n93: #### Scenario: Fallback version when version is None\n94: - **GIVEN** `metadata.version` is `None` or empty\n95: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._increment_version` runs\n96: - **THEN** the version SHALL become `\"0.0.1\"`\n97: \n98: #### Scenario: Version rollback on build failure\n99: - **GIVEN** the version was incremented before the build\n100: - **WHEN** `_build_local` or `_build_cloud` raises an exception\n101: - **THEN** the system SHALL revert `metadata.version` to its original value before re-raising\n102: \n103: ### Requirement: Local Docker build\n104: \n105: The system SHALL build a container image using the local Docker daemon when `build_mode` is `local`.\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: Successful local build\n108: - **GIVEN** Docker is available and the workspace contains a valid `Dockerfile` (generated by `pack`)\n109: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._build_local` runs\n110: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n111:   1. Resolve the image name from metadata (or derive from `agent_name`)\n112:   2. Call `DockerService.build_image` with the workspace `Dockerfile` path\n113:   3. Pass `build_args` containing proxy settings if `--proxy` was provided\n114:   4. Tag the image with the incremented version (default `\"latest\"` if no version)\n115:   5. Return a dict with `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time`\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: Proxy configuration for local build\n118: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--proxy http://proxy.example.com:8080`\n119: - **WHEN** `DockerService.build_image` is called\n120: - **THEN** `build_args` SHALL include `{\"HTTP_PROXY\": \"http://proxy.example.com:8080\", \"HTTPS_PROXY\": \"http://proxy.example.com:8080\"}`\n121: \n122: #### Scenario: Build with custom output path\n123: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--output /tmp/build-artifacts`\n124: - **WHEN** the local build completes\n125: - **THEN** build artifacts (if any) SHALL be saved or referenced at the specified output path\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: Docker build failure\n128: - **GIVEN** the `Dockerfile` has syntax errors or build steps fail\n129: - **WHEN** `DockerService.build_image` is called\n130: - **THEN** it SHALL raise a `docker.errors.BuildError` which propagates through `_handle_error`\n131: \n132: #### Scenario: Image tag from metadata version\n133: - **GIVEN** `metadata.version` is `\"1.2.4\"` after increment\n134: - **WHEN** `_build_local` tags the image\n135: - **THEN** the image SHALL be tagged as `{image_name}:1.2.4`\n136: \n137: ### Requirement: Cloud build\n138: \n139: The system SHALL trigger a remote build on the specified cloud provider when `build_mode` is `cloud`.\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: Cloud build with provider\n142: - **GIVEN** `--cloud-provider huawei` is passed\n143: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._build_cloud` runs\n144: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n145:   1. Authenticate with the cloud provider (using configured credentials)\n146:   2. Upload the workspace contents to the cloud build service\n147:   3. Trigger the build with the specified proxy (if any)\n148:   4. Poll for build completion\n149:   5. Return a dict with cloud build result metadata\n150: \n151: #### Scenario: Cloud build without provider configured\n152: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `cloud` but no `--cloud-provider` is passed and metadata lacks provider config\n153: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._build_cloud` runs\n154: - **THEN** it SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the cloud provider must be specified\n155: \n156: ### Requirement: Build metadata update\n157: \n158: The system SHALL update workspace metadata with build results upon successful completion.\n159: \n160: #### Scenario: Update build metadata on success\n161: - **GIVEN** a successful local or cloud build\n162: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime._update_build_metadata` runs\n163: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n164:   1. Update `metadata.image` with the built image information (`image_name`, `image_id`, `tag`)\n165:   2. Persist the updated metadata to `agent_metadata.yaml` via `MetadataService.save_metadata`\n166:   3. Include `build_time` in the metadata if available\n167: \n168: #### Scenario: Metadata update with custom tag\n169: - **GIVEN** the build succeeded and a specific tag is provided\n170: - **WHEN** `_update_build_metadata` runs with `tag=\"v1.2.4\"`\n171: - **THEN** the metadata `image` field SHALL include `\"tag\": \"v1.2.4\"`\n172: \n173: ### Requirement: CLI success output\n174: \n175: The system SHALL display a Rich-formatted success message after a successful build.\n176: \n177: #### Scenario: Successful build output\n178: - **GIVEN** `BuildRuntime.build` completes without exception\n179: - **WHEN** the `build` command finishes\n180: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print:\n181:   - A success message with the agent name\n182:   - The resolved workspace path\n183:   - The built image name and tag\n184:   - Build duration (if available)\n185:   - Using Rich markup for formatting\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: Verbose build output\n188: - **GIVEN** `--verbose` is passed\n189: - **WHEN** the build runs\n190: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL display detailed logging including:\n191:   - Build mode resolution\n192:   - Prerequisites validation steps\n193:   - Docker build stream output (for local builds)\n194:   - Metadata update confirmation\n195: \n196: ### Requirement: Error handling\n197: \n198: The system SHALL handle build failures gracefully with appropriate error messages.\n199: \n200: #### Scenario: Build error with verbose flag\n201: - **GIVEN** `BuildRuntime.build` raises an exception\n202: - **WHEN** `--verbose` is `True`\n203: - **THEN** `_handle_error` SHALL:\n204:   1. Print `Error building agent: {e}` in red\n205:   2. Print a full traceback\n206:   3. Exit with code `1`\n207: \n208: #### Scenario: Build error without verbose flag\n209: - **GIVEN** `BuildRuntime.build` raises an exception\n210: - **WHEN** `--verbose` is `False`\n211: - **THEN** `_handle_error` SHALL:\n212:   1. Print `Error building agent: {e}` in red\n213:   2. Exit with code `1` (no traceback)\n214: \n215: #### Scenario: Invalid workspace path\n216: - **GIVEN** the workspace path does not exist\n217: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime.build` is called\n218: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` with a message indicating the path is invalid\n219: \n220: ### Requirement: Progress indication\n221: \n222: The system SHALL display a Rich `Progress` spinner during the build operation.\n223: \n224: #### Scenario: Progress spinner during build\n225: - **GIVEN** the build command is running\n226: - **WHEN** `BuildRuntime.build` is executing\n227: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL show a Rich `Progress` spinner with the text `\"Building agent...\"`\n228: \n229: #### Scenario: Progress completion\n230: - **GIVEN** the build completes successfully\n231: - **WHEN** the spinner stops\n232: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL replace the spinner with a success checkmark and summary\n233: \n234: ## File changes\n235: \n236: | Action | File | Description |\n237: |--------|------|-------------|\n238: | Modify | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Add `build` Typer command with options and error handling |\n239: | Modify | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | Implement `build`, `_increment_version`, `_validate_build_prerequisites`, `_build_local`, `_build_cloud`, `_update_build_metadata` |\n240: | Modify | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Implement `build_image` with proxy build_args support |\n241: | Modify | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Ensure `load_metadata` and `save_metadata` support build workflow |\n242: | Modify | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Ensure `BuildRuntime` is exported |\n243: | Add | `tests/cli/test_build.py` | CLI build command tests |\n244: | Add | `tests/runtime/test_build_runtime.py` | BuildRuntime unit tests |\n245: | Add | `tests/services/test_docker_service.py` | DockerService build tests |\n\n(End of file - total 245 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-021: CLI build 命令 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: `build` command entry point\n\nThe system SHALL provide a `build` subcommand on the Typer application that orchestrates container image creation from a previously packaged workspace.\n\n#### Scenario: Command signature and options\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and the user runs `agentcube build --help`\n- **WHEN** the help text is displayed\n- **THEN** it SHALL show the following options:\n  - `-f, --workspace TEXT` — Path to the agent workspace directory (default: `.`)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775853630462,"end":1775853630470}}}}
